{"title":"“改得好”","authors":["石河"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":5,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“改得好”（外一首）石河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么？材料要得太多了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们早就怨声载道……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对！这个问题要调查——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各单位赶快报份材料！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么？文件发得太滥了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"底下早就堆积如山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是！这个问题要解决——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫秘书赶快发个文件！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么？会议泛滥成灾了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众登门老吃闭门羹……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好！这个问题要研究——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在就开会，停止办公！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说我听取意见不虚心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说我改进作风没决心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可是说到做到不放空炮——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“诽谤”领导的，请你当心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“清”官赋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“清”官“清”官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇事不“贪”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不求有功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但求清闲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“清”官“清”官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一“尘”不染："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大事不问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小事不管。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“清”官“清”官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝茶聊天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下班铃响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屁股冒烟……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}